-----------
TUTORIAL 05
-----------

This is a program that reads raw data from AM2302 temperature/humidity sensor
and dislay temperature value using a pair of 7-segments.

*Task* More Data
- show both temperature and humidity

*Task* Simple 'Alarm' Indicator
- modify the code so that an LED will be lit up when temperature is >28deg

*Task* Better precision
- how can we show decimals? without using float!
